1. Write a shell script to print "Hello World".
	-> nano hello.sh
		-> echo "Enter Your Name"
		-> read name
		-> echo "Welcome $name"
	-> chmod 777 hello.sh
	-> bash hello.sh


2. Write a script to display the current date and time.
	-> nano display_Date_Time.sh
		-> echo "Current Date And Time"
		-> date
	-> chmod 777 display_Date_Time.sh
	-> bash display_Date_Time.sh


3. Write a script to check if a file exists.

	echo "Enter filename:"
	read filename

		if [ -f "$filename" ]; then
    			echo "File exists"
		else
    			echo "File does not exist"
	fi



