5. Write a script to add two numbers given by the user.
	-> nano twoSum.sh
		-> echo "Sum of two number"
		-> echo "Enter First Number"
			-> read a
		-> echo "Enter Second Number"
			-> read b 
		-> sum=$((a+b))
		-> echo "Sum of $a and $b is : $sum"
	-> chmod 777 twoSum.sh
	-> bash twoSum.sh



6. Write a script to check if a number is even or odd.
	-> nano isEvenOrOdd.sh
		-> echo "Enter the number: "
		-> read num
		-> if ((num%2 == 0)); then
			echo "$num is even number"
		-> else
			echo "$num is odd"
		
		-> fi

		chmod 777 isEvenOrOdd.sh
		bash isEvenOrOdd.sh


