9. Write a script to check if a user is root.

	user=$(whoami)        // whoami Shows the name of the current user.

	if [ "$user" = "root" ]; then
    		echo "You are root user."
	else
    		echo "You are not root user."
	fi



10. Write a script to print first 10 natural numbers using a loop.

	echo "First 10 Natural Numbers:"

	for ((i=1; i<=10; i++))
		do
    		echo "$i"
	done


	
		

